      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">46.202-3</ph> Standard inspection requirements.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d2655e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d2680e10" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            Standard inspection requirements are contained in the clauses prescribed in <xref href="46.302.dita#FAR_46_302"
                        base="i1072249"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">46.302</xref> through <xref href="46.308.dita#FAR_46_308"
                        base="i1072292"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">46.308</xref>, and in the product and service specifications that are included in solicitations and contracts.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d2680e21" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            The clauses referred to in (a) of this section-</p>
               <ol id="d2655e38" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d2680e27" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
								                Require the contractor to provide and maintain an inspection system that is acceptable to the Government;</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d2680e32" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
								                Give the Government the right to make inspections and tests while work is in process; and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d2680e37" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
								                Require the contractor to keep complete, and make available to the Government, records of its inspection work.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
